## MIT-Licensed Files (Open Core)

The following files are licensed under the MIT License below:

**Domain** (`packages/core/src/humeris/domain/`):
  `orbital_mechanics.py`, `constellation.py`, `coordinate_frames.py`,
  `propagation.py`, `coverage.py`, `access_windows.py`, `ground_track.py`,
  `observation.py`, `omm.py`, `serialization.py`

**Ports** (`packages/core/src/humeris/ports/`): all files

**Adapters** (`packages/core/src/humeris/adapters/`):
  `json_io.py`, `enrichment.py`, `celestrak.py`, `concurrent_celestrak.py`,
  `csv_exporter.py`, `geojson_exporter.py`, `kml_exporter.py`,
  `blender_exporter.py`, `stellarium_exporter.py`, `celestia_exporter.py`,
  `spaceengine_exporter.py`, `ksp_exporter.py`, `ubox_exporter.py`

**CLI**: `packages/core/src/humeris/cli.py`

**Tests**: files whose header says "Licensed under the MIT License"

